cal-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-string\">string</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Initial Value: string = R+30 days</td></tr>#xD;\n<tr style=\"border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: white\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck000.png)\" id=\"item.postflight-debrief.completed\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_blank.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_vjoin_end.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon-q-boolean.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: white; background-color: inherit\" title=\"boolean\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> postflight-debrief.completed</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Debrief Completed</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">0..1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-item-type.html#item-type-boolean\">boolean</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Options Sets</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.overview.sponsor\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.sponsor </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-sponsor-cs#exercise-physiology (\"Exercise Physiology\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.overview.discipline\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.discipline </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-discipline-cs#bone-muscle-exercise (\"Bone/Muscle/Exercise\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-activities.hardware\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-activities.hardware </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#quinton-treadmill (\"Quinton Treadmill\")</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-hardware-cs#cevis (\"CEVIS Cycle Ergometer\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-activities.location\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-activities.location </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-medical-facility-cs#jsc (\"Johnson Space Center\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-fitness-results.test-termination-reason\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-fitness-results.test-termination-reason </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Volitional exhaustion</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Target heart rate achieved</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">ECG abnormality</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Blood pressure response</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Symptoms</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Equipment failure</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.preflight-fitness-results.fitness-category\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for preflight-fitness-results.fitness-category </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Superior</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Excellent</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Good</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Fair</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Poor</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.postflight-fitness-results.deconditioning-assessment\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for postflight-fitness-results.deconditioning-assessment </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Minimal (&lt;5% decline)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Mild (5-10% decline)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Moderate (10-20% decline)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Significant (&gt;20% decline)</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#mmis (\"Medical Mission Information System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
